{"tid":782944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從中國人到香港人　雨革前已支持香港獨立　一位支持者心路歷程","createTime":"2018-08-17T07:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T05:17:15.000Z","uid":47714,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f11214c58f0789b36fea9936cf078d8f3b393c4","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156395895102357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156395895102357&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=41406b34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156395895102357</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n<br />\n有年齡層分野，忘記了是何時，好像幾年前，䁽眼tvb節目，好像是旅遊節目，有個好像海外港人後代女仔還是留學生，她說話用詞對自己是用香港人，說話內容分開香港人、台灣人和中國人，她指會分到，不過更多時候分成亞洲人一群，反而訪問她的老人嘉賓用中國人一詞，那老人好像是馬時享。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n<br />\n我以前有一段很長歲月，長時間流連台灣網路，那時候的我是完全融入台灣網站的環境之中，但有一次，我對於他們說香港的事有反應，我就說香港是怎樣的，反而他們以為我這個留言者假裝香港人，在那一刻，分野在我心中非常強烈，而且這樣的融入，犧牲了一部份的「我」，是在自己不知道事上不作聲。<br />\n<br />\n那時因為長時浸淫在那樣環境和接觸台灣網友，加上常看中國的網站，也有中國的網友，所以非常感受到，香港人是香港人，台灣人是台灣人，中國人是中國人，三種人是互不相同。<br />\n<br />\n我開始支持香港獨立，是在那時的基楚上發展出來的。我在雨傘革命之前就已支持香港獨立，不過那時支持就只是支持，未作為是對香港問題對症下樂的答案去主張和支持香港獨立，那時有人像泛民那樣說沒有香港人支持香港獨立，我就立即說我支持香港獨立，就是這樣明確了我的取態。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n<br />\n其實，我感覺海外港人的情況，似乎跟我有點像，所以我說出我的情況，給大家增加對事情的理解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156392785852357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156392785852357&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=afb06f45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156392785852357</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/PtWJt3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FPtWJt3&h=4a1290a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n其實他說的是事實吧？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBarry Wong:<br />\n好似係，但係本質上中共仍緊握着任命權，所以仍未能完全類比。<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n真係普選，中國又何來任命權啊。選舉權即是人事任命權。<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n928之後果陣泛民同新泛民嘅英文傳媒好癲，成日話香港係中國城市，搞到佢個款好似中國開始有民主咁。我果陣忍佢地，都係因為真係普選、真係民主，權力就喺香港人，唔喺中國政府，而完全實質獨立絕對方便推動完整獨立。"},{"pid":"d8bcc844fc3fa244900c0bdf2285b96521f45124","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d388f694d9233848f42a1463f65ff79281b26f3d","tid":782944,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869059548d91fcd7bafa6cba7357a13b826ead11","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be54984491b834680efe4a5140b5d7973369eabe","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90343bcf587af82b62fb237c46a2df618d7a3d5","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21995be4278399b54cda48f82299346755047e57","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206a4bbab91753e4ac7153d56ea1831da98a3b5d","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T16:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32f63b5c3a78b366d3889b26038bf5a16f35d15","tid":782944,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:38:11.000Z","msg":"係連登唔踩港唔同其他國家比較冇人理㗎啦<br />\n你下次寫個標題做：中國人都有支持港獨 香港人反而認做中國人 香港冇得救<br />\n夠晒juicy，啱晒ig化嘅連登"},{"pid":"0109ec00a49530e62eb562c2338e864ee4d882ad","tid":782944,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T18:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4f84bed0c8aa29217605ab36e28cbf2b078dab","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55f857a9b3f14964d62153930a45c08796b3b3d","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9f48b16747a00cf7da77948ee8503de34b453b","tid":782944,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"雨革之前我就已經支持廣東獨立同港獨喇"},{"pid":"c22d0a40cd484bd9b77ae6a4723f0cd351b1ff4e","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4786dafab1f3edd0d9296eafdf4904c0b129c5ce","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7597217ba2e5d71ef243746e6968261119e450","tid":782944,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}